#13000
@@WNorthwest Watchtower@@N~
@@WYou stand atop the fortified northwest corner of @@BKiess@@W, where the
north and west walls converge into a broad stone platform. A weatherworn
beacon brazier dominates the center, its flames kept burning through every
season by the Wall Command sentries who rotate here in four-hour shifts.
The carved statue of @@WThe Watcher of Storms@@N stands with arms raised
toward the horizon, commemorating the patrols lost to the wildland surges
that plagued Evermeet in its final years. Battle plaques line the inner
parapet wall, each bearing a unit name and a year.@@N
