@@WNorth Wall Walk, West Approach@@N~
@@WThe wall walk narrows slightly here as it nears the gatehouse arch of
the @@WNorth Gate@@N. Iron grates set into the parapet allow wall-walk
defenders to drop materials onto the road below in emergencies. A small
weapons rack bolted to the inside wall holds a pair of longspears in
ready condition, their heads freshly oiled. The city spreads out to the
south in an ordered grid of white stone streets. Voices from the gate
staging yard below drift up on the wind.@@N
