#13005
@@WThe North Gate of @@BKiess@@N~
@@WThe @@WNorth Gate@@N of @@BKiess@@W frames the road in dressed white
stone, its arch carved with the founding date of the compact and the names
of the three governing factions. The @@WWarden's Arch of Confusion Watch@@N
spans the road just inside the gate, a monument honoring forest scouts and
patrol dead whose names fill an iron tablet set into the arch's base.
Route marker stelae on either side point north toward the Forest of
Confusion, their carved arrows freshly re-cut each season. Supply
manifests on iron lecterns flanking the passage detail the last caravan
inventory. Beyond the arch, the @@WNorth Promenade@@N extends south into
the heart of the city.@@N
