@@WNorth Gate Guard Platform@@N~
@@WA broad open platform built over the east side of the @@WNorth Gate@@N
serves as the primary mustering point for gate-shift guards. Tool racks
along the inner wall hold replacement patrol equipment: spears, signal
whistles, and duty rosters in weatherproof cases. A raised watch post
at the outer parapet edge gives a clear view over the approach road.
The platform sees constant foot traffic during shift changes, with
outgoing guards passing their duty notes to arrivals. The wall walk
continues east and west at platform level.@@N
