@@WNorth Promenade, Upper@@N~
@@WThe @@WNorth Promenade@@N begins here at its northern extent, a broad
paved avenue that will carry a traveler all the way south through the
heart of @@BKiess@@W to the South Gate. White stone slabs form the road
surface, each etched along the edges with the name of an Evermeet district
lost to the wildlands. The carved names serve as both memorial and
navigational reference. Lamp posts at even intervals light the avenue
after dark. The staging yard entrance is to the west; Arrival Plaza lies
to the south.@@N
