#13016
kiess street sweeper~
a Kiess street sweeper~
@@WA Kiess street sweeper@@N moves along the avenue, keeping the stones clean.
~
@@WA Kiess street sweeper@@W pushes a wide-headed broom along the stone
street with the steady rhythm of someone working a long shift.
The sweeper wears the public works tabard of the city maintenance
crew and moves with a quiet purposefulness, collecting debris into
a handled box and depositing it at the end of each block. The city's
cleanliness is not accidental; it requires people like this.
~
