#13017
syndic trade courier~
a Syndic trade courier~
@@WA Syndic trade courier@@N moves quickly between destinations.
~
@@WA Syndic trade courier@@W moves at a rapid walk between destinations,
a sealed message satchel over one shoulder and a small route card in
hand. The blue-and-gold of the Trade Syndic insignia is on the satchel
flap. Couriers like this keep the city's commercial information flowing
between the council annex, the market, and the various shop operators.
They do not make eye contact and do not stop unless directly addressed
by someone with obvious authority.
~
