#13019
caravan drover~
a caravan drover~
@@WA caravan drover@@N waits near the wagons, keeping an eye on the team.
~
@@WA caravan drover@@W sits on the wagon tongue or moves between animals
and equipment with the easy patience of someone waiting on a familiar
process. The caravan registration and customs procedure takes time;
drovers learn to rest when the wagon is stopped and move fast when
it isn't. This one has the well-traveled look of someone who knows
Roc Road well in both directions.
~
