#13020
kiess lamplighter~
a Kiess lamplighter~
@@WA Kiess lamplighter@@N tends to the lamp posts on the lane.
~
@@WA Kiess lamplighter@@W works the lamp maintenance route with a long-handled
tool for adjusting wicks and a shoulder-carried oil canister. The work
is unglamorous but essential: Kiess's lamp density is higher than most
cities, and the lamp crew keeps that system functioning through rotation
and consistent maintenance. This lamplighter works with the comfortable
efficiency of someone who has done this particular stretch hundreds of times.
~
