forest confusion scout~
a Forest Confusion scout~
@@WA Forest Confusion scout@@N moves with the alert bearing of a recent returnee.
~
@@WA Forest Confusion scout@@W carries field equipment that shows genuine
use: worn straps, chalked markers on the map case, and a short
blade with a practical edge rather than a display finish. Scouts
returning from the Forest of Confusion carry a combination of
wariness and information that Kiess specifically needs. This one
is making their way toward the debriefing post but is not in a rush
that suggests urgency.
~
